{
  "stem": "268.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was the-- the big change was September 1, 1939.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a-- the abrupt change, a sudden change.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was not a gradual, something you get prepared.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As far as-- you mean changes prior to the outbreak of the war, when the war broke out, the changes?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Our first awakening, the actual, both your physical and mental awakening was September 1, 1939, on a Friday morning.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You could wake me tomorrow morning at three in the morning or two and ask me, Henry, when did a war break out.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I can tell you the time and the day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because it's so cemented in my mind.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that was the rude and shocking awakening of explosion, bomb, or bombs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because the windows began to rattle, almost like a earthquake or more so.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we jumped out of bed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was before dawn or right at dawn, Friday morning, September first.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My parents started to-- turned on the light quick.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Looking out the window, we could see smoke.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my father said, oh, my god, a war broke out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Then another bomb and another explosion.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I could see out of my bed, ashen faces, white faces.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And, as a kid, yeah, I wasn't so affected right away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "In fact, I remember-- which seems silly now-- I remember thinking to myself, wow, this is-- this could be exciting.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Until now, I used to see it in the movies.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Wayne-- John Wayne, with cavalry, and Rover 1 pictures with explosions on the western front and all that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And here we're seeing it live.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And the next thought came to my mind, hey, Monday-- school year is supposed to start Monday.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I was supposed to go in the ninth grade.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "No school Monday.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
